<p>As a MATIC holder, your active participation in staking not only contributes to the security and efficiency of the network but also entitles you to staking rewards. These rewards serve as an incentive for you to lock up your MATIC tokens, thus reducing the circulating supply and potentially driving up the token&#8217;s value. </p>



